{"tid":160650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE中文口試題目以下兩樣食物哪樣更能象徵人生","createTime":"2017-03-18T02:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T04:16:36.000Z","uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6345ca34de33bbe1b5263a33d09d88e7741626b","tid":160650,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"苦瓜           洋蔥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be33ce37c5f4586edfdeec45a34a24f9c1328d7","tid":160650,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:10:44.000Z","msg":"苦瓜<br />\n<br />\n你講半世瓜故事5硬"},{"pid":"3137c7d70b8845132fdd8c3d752dac3ebed98276","tid":160650,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T02:13:08.000Z","msg":"同檸檬茶果篇差唔多解讀 好易下喎"},{"pid":"1c3c42fded7e6c650b2ba66ec36f8ea27719a552","tid":160650,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>苦瓜<br />\n<br />\n你講半世瓜故事5硬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只係講一樣但無比較肥硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">更</span>能夠」即係兩樣都可以比喻到人生，只係一種苦中帶甜，另一種甜中有辣。<br />\n<br />\n除咗味道之外，外形、氣味、特性都可以比較，仲要帶出同人生相似嘅特點。<br />\n<br />\n總之就要<span style=\"color: red;\">比較</span>同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">比喻</span>。 整體黎講，檸檬茶之後好多人對呢類型題目操到熟哂，又唔會好深奧或者好抽象，算係易嘅題目但有少少伏位（似係考你細心同閱讀理解）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef490632fbc1c4a1deaa30db00e193b150d25b8","tid":160650,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}